snippet.title: PC Longplay [776] Need For Speed II SE
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: mihaibest  

This is the 3dfx version. I win all 7 races in tournament mode, then i also play and win the 8th bonus track. At the end i also show all car videos.
Overall, i think this game was much better than nfs1, its enjoyable to play and it doesnt seem unfair like the first one. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
